1
00:01:29,720 --> 00:01:32,830
[Cage of Shadows]

2
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:36,090
[Episode 5]

3
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,039
Master.

4
00:01:45,990 --> 00:01:46,950
It's you.

5
00:01:47,990 --> 00:01:49,320
What are you doing here?

6
00:01:57,360 --> 00:01:59,479
You mean she didn't kill you?

7
00:02:00,250 --> 00:02:02,650
Now that I see you're all right,
I can relax.

8
00:02:07,290 --> 00:02:08,360
You mean

9
00:02:08,539 --> 00:02:09,740
she brought you here?

10
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:12,520
Then I guess

11
00:02:13,040 --> 00:02:14,470
she sent you to keep an eye on me

12
00:02:14,470 --> 00:02:16,470
so I wouldn't do anything reckless.

13
00:02:20,420 --> 00:02:21,260
Qi?

14
00:02:24,300 --> 00:02:25,300
That's your name?

15
00:02:27,370 --> 00:02:29,510
Then I'll just call you Qi from now on.

16
00:02:42,270 --> 00:02:43,910
Tomorrow's exam questions?

17
00:02:45,070 --> 00:02:46,410
How did you get this?

18
00:02:50,300 --> 00:02:52,100
Did she ask you to give this to me?

19
00:02:58,310 --> 00:03:00,030
On Choosing a Husband...

20
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:09,560
In the eyes of the world,

21
00:03:09,580 --> 00:03:10,960
once a woman comes of age,

22
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:13,080
the most important matter in her life
is choosing a husband.

23
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,320
I have already taught you much

24
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:16,680
about the principles women
are expected to follow

25
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:18,340
and the proper way to conduct yourselves.

26
00:03:18,340 --> 00:03:20,770
Based on what you have learned,

27
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:22,800
write an essay on the subject

28
00:03:22,880 --> 00:03:24,140
of choosing a husband.

29
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:25,079
You will have 2 hours

30
00:03:25,079 --> 00:03:26,480
to complete the exam.

31
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:27,940
Unless you turn in your paper,

32
00:03:27,940 --> 00:03:29,640
you may not leave the examination hall.

33
00:03:29,640 --> 00:03:30,920
You may begin.

34
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:37,220
[On Choosing a Husband]

35
00:03:45,880 --> 00:03:47,420
Everyone will remain here

36
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:49,260
for the next 2 hours.

37
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:52,680
This is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity.

38
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,660
At this rate, just copying
all of this down

39
00:04:15,660 --> 00:04:17,579
will take until
it's time to hand in the paper.

40
00:04:17,579 --> 00:04:19,980
How am I supposed to investigate anything?

41
00:04:40,780 --> 00:04:42,680
[Teammate]

42
00:04:50,110 --> 00:04:51,310
What is she doing?

43
00:04:51,409 --> 00:04:53,330
Is she turning in a blank exam paper?

44
00:04:53,330 --> 00:04:54,860
She's totally unreliable.

45
00:04:54,990 --> 00:04:55,790
Wait.

46
00:05:01,080 --> 00:05:02,250
What is it, Madam?

47
00:05:02,470 --> 00:05:03,950
Didn't I just say

48
00:05:04,060 --> 00:05:05,300
that no one is allowed

49
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,940
to leave the examination hall
during the exam?

50
00:05:06,940 --> 00:05:07,660
Madam,

51
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,220
I've already finished my paper.

52
00:05:09,220 --> 00:05:10,810
Are you certain
you're handing it in just like this?

53
00:05:10,810 --> 00:05:12,260
I've already finished my paper.

54
00:05:12,260 --> 00:05:13,570
Am I not allowed to turn it in?

55
00:05:13,570 --> 00:05:16,130
Do you know what happens to those

56
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:18,380
who don't take the exam seriously?

57
00:05:18,380 --> 00:05:19,740
I did take it seriously.

58
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,820
Everything I wanted to say—

59
00:05:21,820 --> 00:05:23,670
and could say—on this topic

60
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,050
is already on the paper.

61
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,970
Unless I misheard
or overlooked something,

62
00:05:26,970 --> 00:05:29,290
I don't believe you specified
a minimum word count, Madam.

63
00:05:29,290 --> 00:05:31,150
You'd better think this through.

64
00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:33,090
Once you leave this examination hall,

65
00:05:33,090 --> 00:05:34,250
it'll be too late

66
00:05:34,580 --> 00:05:35,800
to regret.

67
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:39,050
Thank you for the reminder, Madam.

68
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:00,900
She's really impossible to count on.

69
00:06:12,510 --> 00:06:15,940
[Teammate]

70
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:32,120
I'm already out.

71
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:33,780
There's no way I'm going back.

72
00:06:34,010 --> 00:06:35,400
If you make any more noise,

73
00:06:35,400 --> 00:06:37,200
you'll only get me into trouble.

74
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:39,840
I know what I'm doing.

75
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:40,520
Let's go.

76
00:06:50,830 --> 00:06:52,320
The moment I approached this place
last night,

77
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:53,310
I was stopped.

78
00:06:54,180 --> 00:06:56,980
There must be something
suspicious going on here.

79
00:07:00,880 --> 00:07:03,200
Looks like there's something
hidden underneath.

80
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:04,140
I'll go down and take a look.

81
00:07:04,140 --> 00:07:05,340
Keep an eye out for me.

82
00:07:05,740 --> 00:07:06,420
It's fine.

83
00:08:49,040 --> 00:08:51,700
Looks like she's obsessed
with being a teacher.

84
00:08:55,330 --> 00:08:56,250
Master.

85
00:08:56,270 --> 00:08:57,660
I don't like being lied to.

86
00:08:57,660 --> 00:08:59,050
Can you at least give me
some peace of mind?

87
00:08:59,050 --> 00:09:00,010
Master,

88
00:09:00,300 --> 00:09:01,450
things have already come to this point.

89
00:09:01,450 --> 00:09:02,400
Either keep me by your side

90
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:03,830
and let me act under your watch,

91
00:09:03,830 --> 00:09:05,320
or keep everything from me

92
00:09:05,470 --> 00:09:07,180
and let me learn things
the hard way myself.

93
00:09:07,180 --> 00:09:08,690
The worst that can happen is I die.

94
00:09:08,690 --> 00:09:10,090
How dare you threaten me?

95
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,790
Master...

96
00:09:23,040 --> 00:09:23,960
Master...

97
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,000
W-What

98
00:09:25,330 --> 00:09:25,990
is this?

99
00:09:26,860 --> 00:09:29,250
The toxin has already reached
the back of the brain.

100
00:09:29,250 --> 00:09:30,580
She won't wake up again.

101
00:09:35,330 --> 00:09:36,290
The antidote.

102
00:09:36,310 --> 00:09:37,840
The antidote for my mother!

103
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:50,980
I've already checked.

104
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:52,480
The antidote isn't here.

105
00:09:54,070 --> 00:09:54,870
Look at this.

106
00:09:55,830 --> 00:09:56,370
[No. 5]

107
00:09:56,370 --> 00:09:56,850
[No. 4]

108
00:09:56,850 --> 00:09:57,360
[No. 3]

109
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,070
[No. 2]

110
00:09:57,680 --> 00:09:58,770
These...

111
00:09:58,120 --> 00:10:00,210
[No. 1]

112
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,440
Could these be...

113
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:01,360
That's right.

114
00:10:02,280 --> 00:10:03,800
Different rankings

115
00:10:04,030 --> 00:10:05,830
are given different medicines.

116
00:10:06,630 --> 00:10:07,460
[No. 1]

117
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:08,920
No wonder some of them are unconscious,

118
00:10:08,920 --> 00:10:10,600
while others are already like puppets.

119
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:12,140
They're using people as test subjects.

120
00:10:12,140 --> 00:10:15,000
All the students on this floor
have become their drugged puppets.

121
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:16,200
And that's precisely

122
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:18,680
how Lingya Tower controls

123
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:21,170
those so-called nobles—with these drugs.

124
00:10:21,170 --> 00:10:23,400
This medicine causes hallucinations,

125
00:10:23,420 --> 00:10:25,640
making people feel as if they've entered
a state of ultimate bliss—

126
00:10:25,640 --> 00:10:27,760
so intense it's almost uncontrollable.

127
00:10:27,760 --> 00:10:29,090
Once they've tasted it,

128
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:31,170
they become hooked on the feeling.

129
00:10:31,410 --> 00:10:32,120
[No. 1]

130
00:10:33,880 --> 00:10:35,470
And this is supposed to be a reward

131
00:10:35,470 --> 00:10:36,490
for the top-ranked student?

132
00:10:36,490 --> 00:10:38,250
These drugs may be addictive,

133
00:10:38,280 --> 00:10:40,460
but at least those
who take them still retain some sanity.

134
00:10:40,460 --> 00:10:41,380
The other drugs

135
00:10:42,160 --> 00:10:43,040
are even worse.

136
00:10:43,210 --> 00:10:45,770
If they were all nothing but puppets,

137
00:10:46,550 --> 00:10:48,850
she probably wouldn't get
her fill as a teacher.

138
00:10:48,850 --> 00:10:51,370
So she lets the high-performing
students keep their minds,

139
00:10:51,370 --> 00:10:53,050
while the weaker ones

140
00:10:53,450 --> 00:10:54,740
are reduced to toys

141
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:56,620
for her to manipulate at will.

142
00:11:02,610 --> 00:11:03,650
I get it now.

143
00:11:03,940 --> 00:11:05,320
Qin Yuren controls those puppets

144
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:06,600
through the sound of bells.

145
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:07,840
Maybe we can use that against her.

146
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:09,800
Let's set Qin Yuren aside for now.

147
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:11,200
Shouldn't you

148
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:13,540
be taking your exam right now?

149
00:11:14,590 --> 00:11:15,680
I've already finished my exam.

150
00:11:15,680 --> 00:11:17,080
That fast?

151
00:11:17,310 --> 00:11:18,690
Even a seasoned ghostwriter

152
00:11:18,690 --> 00:11:21,480
would need quite a while to copy
all those essays I gave you.

153
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:23,540
How could you possibly be out so soon?

154
00:11:24,560 --> 00:11:26,040
I only wrote one sentence.

155
00:11:26,060 --> 00:11:27,060
One sentence?

156
00:11:28,330 --> 00:11:31,060
Qin Yuren has always
valued order in the academy.

157
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:32,800
What you did

158
00:11:32,800 --> 00:11:34,280
was utterly disrespectful—

159
00:11:34,280 --> 00:11:37,080
you practically stomped her dignity
into the mud.

160
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:38,870
Master, don't worry.

161
00:11:38,890 --> 00:11:40,560
I really did
answer the question seriously.

162
00:11:40,560 --> 00:11:42,200
She asked us to write

163
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:43,360
about choosing a husband,

164
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:44,720
and what I most

165
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:46,160
wanted to say was this...

166
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:48,330
[On Choosing a Husband]

167
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:48,650
"I'd rather grow old clinging
to a fragrant branch

168
00:11:48,650 --> 00:11:51,380
than dance with yellow leaves
in the autumn wind."

169
00:11:51,380 --> 00:11:52,620
Everyone says

170
00:11:52,760 --> 00:11:53,820
choosing a husband

171
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:56,340
is the most important thing
in a woman's life,

172
00:11:56,340 --> 00:11:57,490
that becoming a wife

173
00:11:57,520 --> 00:11:59,200
is the only path

174
00:11:59,220 --> 00:12:00,620
available to her.

175
00:12:00,650 --> 00:12:01,520
I don't agree.

176
00:12:01,550 --> 00:12:03,090
I insist on walking my own path,

177
00:12:03,090 --> 00:12:04,680
even if it means going against tradition.

178
00:12:04,680 --> 00:12:05,680
Choose a husband?

179
00:12:07,370 --> 00:12:08,460
I refuse.

180
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:09,320
She is...

181
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:10,820
rather interesting.

182
00:12:12,370 --> 00:12:14,380
If you hadn't met in Lingya Tower,

183
00:12:14,410 --> 00:12:15,370
perhaps

184
00:12:15,670 --> 00:12:17,350
the two of you might have

185
00:12:17,520 --> 00:12:18,670
become kindred spirits and talked
through the night by candlelight.

186
00:12:18,670 --> 00:12:21,110
That Qin Yuren is arrogant
and cold-blooded.

187
00:12:21,110 --> 00:12:22,710
I wouldn't want
to exchange a single word with her.

188
00:12:22,710 --> 00:12:25,230
Actually, Qin Yuren
was never a truly wicked person.

189
00:12:25,230 --> 00:12:26,770
She was held back by her feelings,

190
00:12:26,770 --> 00:12:29,060
and later struck
by a terrible twist of fate.

191
00:12:29,060 --> 00:12:31,060
That's how she became who she is now.

192
00:12:33,300 --> 00:12:34,500
Master,

193
00:12:34,530 --> 00:12:35,450
are you saying

194
00:12:36,740 --> 00:12:38,140
you know her background?

195
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:43,880
[Elite Academy]

196
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:50,020
How did the exam go?

197
00:12:50,020 --> 00:12:50,950
Not bad, I guess.

198
00:12:51,130 --> 00:12:51,770
Yanzhi,

199
00:12:52,160 --> 00:12:53,080
where did you go?

200
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:55,210
I've been looking everywhere for you.

201
00:12:56,600 --> 00:12:57,840
What are we going to do?

202
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,440
Dao really seems determined

203
00:12:59,440 --> 00:13:01,300
to team up with those two sisters.

204
00:13:01,880 --> 00:13:02,940
Then what about us?

205
00:13:03,570 --> 00:13:05,370
It's fine. Don't worry about it.

206
00:13:10,640 --> 00:13:11,770
The results are out!

207
00:13:14,550 --> 00:13:16,850
[Elite Academy Competition Rankings]

208
00:13:20,820 --> 00:13:21,360
[No. 2 Bai Xiaohui]

209
00:13:21,110 --> 00:13:22,270
I'm second again.

210
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:22,220
[No. 3 Bai Xiaoying]

211
00:13:22,270 --> 00:13:23,720
I'm third again.

212
00:13:23,550 --> 00:13:24,800
[No. 1 Nan Yanzhi]

213
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:24,920
Yanzhi,

214
00:13:25,160 --> 00:13:26,480
you got first place!

215
00:13:26,500 --> 00:13:28,300
You actually took the top spot!

216
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:29,800
You're amazing, Yanzhi!

217
00:13:29,800 --> 00:13:31,340
What's the point of her doing well

218
00:13:31,340 --> 00:13:34,200
when she's stuck with a teammate
dragging her down?

219
00:13:37,400 --> 00:13:39,360
I came in last.

220
00:13:41,800 --> 00:13:43,060
This isn't your fault.

221
00:13:43,560 --> 00:13:45,420
If Madam liked my paper,

222
00:13:45,450 --> 00:13:48,300
then she clearly wasn't looking
for conventional approaches.

223
00:13:48,300 --> 00:13:50,630
But our group could've taken first place.

224
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:53,240
It's because my score was so low

225
00:13:53,280 --> 00:13:54,900
that I dragged everyone down.

226
00:13:54,900 --> 00:13:55,740
Look,

227
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:56,910
it's Dao's name.

228
00:13:56,870 --> 00:13:58,320
[No. 4 Dao]

229
00:13:57,020 --> 00:13:58,810
Dao did pretty well, didn't she?

230
00:13:58,810 --> 00:14:00,050
Of course.

231
00:14:00,160 --> 00:14:02,160
Our Dao did exceptionally well.

232
00:14:02,160 --> 00:14:04,320
The three of us are definitely
going to come out on top this time.

233
00:14:04,320 --> 00:14:05,520
Dao,

234
00:14:06,040 --> 00:14:07,820
are you really not teaming up
with us anymore?

235
00:14:07,820 --> 00:14:08,900
You two...

236
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:10,230
You are hopelessly dumb,

237
00:14:10,230 --> 00:14:11,130
and she turned in her paper early.

238
00:14:11,130 --> 00:14:11,830
Well...

239
00:14:11,960 --> 00:14:13,420
Can you really blame me?

240
00:14:13,890 --> 00:14:15,210
I trust all of you

241
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:17,170
are already aware of your results.

242
00:14:17,540 --> 00:14:18,980
Next, I will announce

243
00:14:19,010 --> 00:14:20,770
the final group rankings.

244
00:14:20,620 --> 00:14:24,790
[Elite Academy Competition Rankings]

245
00:14:20,800 --> 00:14:23,560
There were 20 students
taking the exam this round,

246
00:14:23,560 --> 00:14:25,280
so it was impossible to divide everyone
evenly into groups of three.

247
00:14:25,280 --> 00:14:26,160
As a result,

248
00:14:26,390 --> 00:14:28,440
2 students were left without a group.

249
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:30,280
Their group total score
was at a disadvantage,

250
00:14:30,280 --> 00:14:32,300
but fortunately, the 2 of them
scored high enough

251
00:14:32,210 --> 00:14:33,800
[Elite Academy Competition Rankings]

252
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:34,560
that they didn't end up near the bottom.

253
00:14:35,850 --> 00:14:38,450
Bai Xiaohui, Bai Xiaoying—

254
00:14:38,500 --> 00:14:41,040
you were the two left without a group.

255
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:44,820
Don't look at me like that.

256
00:14:45,290 --> 00:14:47,890
I can't stand self-righteous people
like you.

257
00:14:52,010 --> 00:14:53,570
The 3 of us came up here together,

258
00:14:53,570 --> 00:14:54,920
so naturally we're a team.

259
00:14:54,920 --> 00:14:56,560
How did you get tomorrow's exam questions?

260
00:14:56,560 --> 00:14:57,640
You don't need to worry about that.

261
00:14:57,640 --> 00:14:58,900
Just focus on the exam.

262
00:14:58,960 --> 00:15:00,690
What do you want me to do for you?

263
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:01,760
Nothing more.

264
00:15:02,400 --> 00:15:03,980
Didn't we come up here together?

265
00:15:03,980 --> 00:15:05,290
It's only natural that we help each other.

266
00:15:05,290 --> 00:15:07,290
Then why not give the exam questions

267
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:08,560
to Jiang Man?

268
00:15:11,020 --> 00:15:12,330
Jiang Man isn't strong enough
academically.

269
00:15:12,330 --> 00:15:13,890
If she suddenly scores too well,

270
00:15:13,890 --> 00:15:16,490
Qin Yuren will definitely
become suspicious.

271
00:15:18,240 --> 00:15:19,000
I know

272
00:15:19,280 --> 00:15:21,880
you're always on guard
around the people here,

273
00:15:22,430 --> 00:15:24,890
but as long as you still see me
as a companion,

274
00:15:25,120 --> 00:15:27,180
I'll stand by you through everything

275
00:15:27,510 --> 00:15:29,570
and treat you with complete honesty.

276
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:33,280
How can you go back
on your word like this?

277
00:15:33,280 --> 00:15:34,320
You have no integrity at all!

278
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:35,360
Shameless!

279
00:15:35,360 --> 00:15:36,420
You're a disgrace!

280
00:15:37,320 --> 00:15:39,380
I never promised you anything
in the first place.

281
00:15:39,380 --> 00:15:40,420
I already told you

282
00:15:40,450 --> 00:15:41,710
to stay away from me.

283
00:15:41,760 --> 00:15:43,600
You're the ones
who kept getting your hopes up.

284
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:44,080
You...

285
00:15:44,080 --> 00:15:44,880
Enough.

286
00:15:46,160 --> 00:15:47,160
The groups have already been decided,

287
00:15:47,160 --> 00:15:48,160
so further discussion is pointless.

288
00:15:48,160 --> 00:15:51,360
Next, I will announce the top-ranked group
for this exam.

289
00:15:52,220 --> 00:15:53,760
Let us congratulate the three of them.

290
00:15:53,760 --> 00:15:54,520
Wait,

291
00:15:55,160 --> 00:15:56,000
Madam!

292
00:15:56,620 --> 00:15:58,130
I suddenly remembered something—

293
00:15:58,130 --> 00:16:00,410
I seem to have left something out.

294
00:16:00,430 --> 00:16:01,380
What did you leave out?

295
00:16:01,380 --> 00:16:03,600
I forgot to write my name
on my exam paper.

296
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:05,240
So my result for this exam

297
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:07,850
shouldn't count.

298
00:16:09,660 --> 00:16:11,630
Nan Yanzhi, have you lost your mind?

299
00:16:11,630 --> 00:16:13,010
Exactly, Yanzhi!

300
00:16:15,040 --> 00:16:17,650
Are you treating the Elite Academy exams

301
00:16:17,680 --> 00:16:19,160
as a joke?

302
00:16:22,160 --> 00:16:22,990
Madam,

303
00:16:23,400 --> 00:16:26,320
it's precisely because
I take the exam seriously

304
00:16:26,340 --> 00:16:27,980
that I chose to admit it.

305
00:16:28,120 --> 00:16:29,320
But this academy

306
00:16:29,320 --> 00:16:30,810
was never truly an academy,

307
00:16:30,810 --> 00:16:32,680
and you were never truly a teacher.

308
00:16:32,680 --> 00:16:34,020
So perhaps an omission like this

309
00:16:34,020 --> 00:16:35,950
is hardly worth making a fuss over.

310
00:16:37,560 --> 00:16:38,360
Very well.

311
00:16:39,170 --> 00:16:40,960
As a reward for your honesty,

312
00:16:41,440 --> 00:16:42,760
I'll grant your wish.

313
00:16:43,840 --> 00:16:44,440
Guards!

314
00:16:45,040 --> 00:16:46,240
This student's attitude is unacceptable.

315
00:16:46,240 --> 00:16:47,110
Her results are invalidated.

316
00:16:47,110 --> 00:16:47,720
What are you doing?

317
00:16:47,720 --> 00:16:49,050
Her results are voided.

318
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:50,180
What are you doing?

319
00:16:50,480 --> 00:16:51,540
Let go of me!

320
00:17:00,970 --> 00:17:03,060
[First Meeting]

321
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:04,319
Please...

322
00:17:04,319 --> 00:17:05,440
don't kill me!

323
00:17:43,240 --> 00:17:44,080
Nan Yanzhi,

324
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:46,300
you're so soft-hearted,

325
00:17:46,300 --> 00:17:47,720
and you still want revenge?

326
00:17:47,720 --> 00:17:48,340
Master,

327
00:17:48,440 --> 00:17:49,720
please give me one more chance.

328
00:17:49,720 --> 00:17:51,250
I'll go kill him right now.

329
00:17:51,480 --> 00:17:52,600
Yanzhi,

330
00:17:53,200 --> 00:17:54,130
there's no need.

331
00:17:54,850 --> 00:17:56,410
You're too kind by nature.

332
00:17:56,880 --> 00:17:58,960
Lingya Tower is not a place
for someone like you.

333
00:17:58,960 --> 00:17:59,960
But Master,

334
00:18:00,120 --> 00:18:01,920
my mother was poisoned by Lingya Tower.

335
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:03,520
I have to get the antidote!

